itools.catalog
==============

The abort method has been renamed to abort_changes.
**Catalog.abort => Catalog.abort_changes**

The make_catalog method don't take anymore the fields in parameter.
The fields parameter is replaced by the method CatalogAware.get_catalog_fields.
It is not necessary to inherit from ikaaro.Root class to define the catalog fields now.

get_catalog_indexes method has been replaced by get_catalog_values. This method
returns a dictionary with the values of the fields to be indexed.

**make_catalog(uri, *fields) => make_catalog(uri)**
** => CatalogAware.get_catalog_fields **
**CatalogAware.get_catalog_indexes => CatalogAware.get_catalog_values**


itools.csv
==========

Remove advanced feature "IntegerKey" (use the Table handler instead).
The Row.set_value method has been replaced by update_row.
Its functioning is similar to method itools.table.update_record.
But changed values only must be specified.

**Remove IntegerKey**
**Replace "Row.set_value" by "CSVFile.update_row"**


